## 2. Game Assets (3D Models, Textures, Shaders, Audio, Animations)

**ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.**

All game assets, including but not limited to 3D models, textures, shaders,
audio files, animations, prefabs, materials, VFX graphs, URP settings, and
visual art assets, are protected by copyright law. No part of these assets
may be reproduced, distributed, modified, or transmitted in any form without
the prior written permission of the copyright holder.

**Prior to version 0.0.50,** game assets were licensed under CC BY-NC-ND 4.0.
**As of version 0.0.50 (July 2026),** all game assets are All Rights Reserved.
Copies of the repository made before this version retain their original
CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 rights for those specific assets as they existed at that time.

### Exceptions — Third-Party Assets

Some assets are sourced from third parties and retain their original licenses.
These are **not** governed by the ARR terms above:

| Source       | License                | Location                         |
|--------------|------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Poly Haven   | CC0 1.0 (Public Domain)| Textures, HDRI (various folders) |
| Mixamo       | Adobe Mixamo License   | Character animations             |
